---
title: Sticky Chinese-Style Beef Strip Noodles with Plum-Oyster Baby Broccoli & Shredded Cabbage
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan (and your stomach!) for this Chinese-style dish where beef strips, veggies and udon noodles take centre stage. With a sprinkling of fresh parsley for a boost of flavour, you’ll be slurping your way to noodle nirvana in no time!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

